name: 250 (500) logos of tech products
description:
Here's a file with logos of 250 tech companies in two variations each–glyph and wordmark. Each logo is a vector that can be exported in any size, all of the logos are conveniently created as variants for easy swapping.


All of the apps, included in this file are listed on companies.tools–it's where tech teams share which apps they use to work on their product. The file will be updated accordingly to the products, listed on the website.
